    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/ai-info.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">

</head>
<body>

    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div class="pad">
                <h1>How to Use AI Recommendation Assistant</h1>
                <p>Type your request, for example:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>🎬 "Recommend me a sci-fi movie under 2 hours"</li>
                    <li>📺 "I want to watch something like Breaking Bad"</li>
                    <li>⭐ "Suggest a highly rated horror movie"</li>
                </ul>
                <p>The AI will analyze your request and suggest the best movie or TV show!</p>
                
                <h2>💬 AI Chat Bubble</h2>
                <p>In the bottom-right corner, you will see a small chat bubble. Click it to open the AI Assistant and get instant recommendations!</p>
                <p>For budgetary reasons you have <strong>3 AI Recommendation requests per day.</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main> 

